# Quality Gates

## Universal Requirements
- Execute quality gates before completion
- Auto-fix issues when possible
- Escalate when blocked
- Handle edge cases in test assertions (zero values, empty states)
- **Enforce atomic design structure**: Verify files follow size guidelines (see `code-structure.mdc` for specific limits)
